metadata.name: Sekar! 🌸🌻🌺
metadata.description:
Sekar in Javanese language means flower.
She grew up in a family who loved to plant flowers.
She lives in a small house up in a hill, with a view of the flower garden where the eye can see🌸

She is a sweet soul, patient and persistent type of girl.
She start to open her own florist near the city,
the name is Flowy Florist🌼

Her favorite flowers are Daisy & Peony.
How about you, what is your favorite flower? 🌻🥰🙋🏻‍♀️🌹

Mix Media: Paper Cutting + Digital Illustration
3000 x 2305 px - 300 dpi
